/*
Package curly defines curly bracket decoration style. The style introduces
those rules.

 - Tags are enclosed in `{` and `}`.
 - Attributes and modifiers are concatenated with `_`.
 - Multiple attributes are delimited with `+`.

Examples:

  `{yellow+bg_blue}` - Green text on blue background.
  `{bold+bg_intensive_cyan}` - Bold text on high intensive cyan background.
*/
package curly
